translation.Name: Buak_Note_16
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: I absolutely knew the brainwash tech would be the real winner! Hah, look at me now! Mr. Zakerson, a true and deserving higher-up! I’ve got a car that starts when I want it to, a house without a leaky water stained roof, and soon enough, I’ll be running my own lab!
